### Stock Service API Endpoints
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or JetBrains IDEs

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8001

### Get stock data with trailing slash and stock_code parameter
GET {{baseUrl}}/stock/?stock_code=aapl.us
Accept: application/json

### Get stock data without trailing slash and stock_code parameter
GET {{baseUrl}}/stock?stock_code=aapl.us
Accept: application/json

### Test various parameter names

# Using 'q' parameter (compatible with API service)
GET {{baseUrl}}/stock?q=aapl.us
Accept: application/json

# Using 'symbol' parameter (alternative name)
GET {{baseUrl}}/stock?symbol=aapl.us
Accept: application/json

### Test various stock symbols

# Microsoft
GET {{baseUrl}}/stock?stock_code=msft.us
Accept: application/json

# Google
GET {{baseUrl}}/stock?stock_code=goog.us
Accept: application/json

# Amazon
GET {{baseUrl}}/stock?stock_code=amzn.us
Accept: application/json

# Tesla
GET {{baseUrl}}/stock?stock_code=tsla.us
Accept: application/json

# Facebook/Meta
GET {{baseUrl}}/stock?stock_code=meta.us
Accept: application/json

# Netflix
GET {{baseUrl}}/stock?stock_code=nflx.us
Accept: application/json

### Error cases

# Invalid stock symbol
GET {{baseUrl}}/stock?stock_code=invalid
Accept: application/json

# Missing parameter (should return 400 Bad Request)
GET {{baseUrl}}/stock
Accept: application/json